result.name: Hung Hom Cafe

reviews.text: The set meals come up with a soup, a rice and a drink. The dishes are taste good and the amount of food should be well enough for an ordinary man, so it is better to order 3 dishes for 4 ladies with an extra drink. You may order a food box to take away the food in case of ordering too much dishes.

For me this place served me super breakfast with hk36... Set menu... super yummy nice coffee delicious tomato macaroni very reasonable price.. cozy place quite spacy (Hong Kong) man....
...

Reasonably priced. Special meals menu also available. Big portions. I ordered a red bean drink and the red beans were too hard so didn't have any taste. The food was okay but it didn't have the WOW factor.
The last time I order the salad, and find that the chicken wings were raw. Not only that, the staff were really rude, the environment is very noisy and dirty, I will never come again.

Nice big portion foods with reasonable price.  Choose set menus with drinks could save few bucks. But the foods are a little bit salty. The atmosphere in the restaurant is also nice. A good place to have meals if you are around and have no idea what to eat.

result.name: 紅磡冰室

reviews.text: 食物及服務員、衛生都很好，去第—次巳好好印象，希望不要像已有名氣及上市的餐廰，愈做愈差
店內廚房師父手勢 OK 另早餐多選擇非常之好（撐）
份量很大感覺是外面的兩倍，兩個人吃一份可能就會飽，價格也不貴算是蠻划算的，服務人員不像評價說的那麼糟，甚至還招待了湯品，是一次愉快的用餐經驗！
好多卡位，食物水準可以。在尖沙咀價格合理
